I never thought I would be 30 and single, but looking back on this year I’m glad that I took the time to focus on myself, my mental health, and celebrate my growth along the way. Join me in celebrating YOU with @visiblemobile!  Get your own Visible unlimited plan on Verizon for just $30/mo. #visiblepartner 

Quick year in review:

1. This was from a year ago. I didn’t know how yet, but I knew my life was going to change. I knew opportunities were coming my way and all I wanted to do was to live and grow throughout the process. 
2. A life long dream came true for me being on my favorite game show. I never envisioned it happening like this but I’m so grateful that it did. 
3. I was able to guest star on tour and finally travel across the east coast meeting amazing people and showcasing who I am, what I’m capable of and making an audience laugh while doing it.
4. Lastly, this is one year later. I stand confident knowing who I am, what I want, and what I bring to the table. Needless to say, I remain humble and hopeful for the new year. I’m so thankful for all the lessons I’ve learned along the way and the growing I still have left to do.

Santa Rod 🎅🏽 Thank you so much to @heartmattersffa for allowing me to handout gifts to the kids this year! This is the first time I’ve ever dressed as Santa and I’m so honored to have done it at their annual family Christmas event. The amount of “skinny Santa” and “you need to eat more cookies” comments had me dying 😂 their little smiles and excitement from receiving their big bag of gifts was the best finish to this year that I could ask for. Merry Christmas and happy holidays from Santa Rod!🎄

ROD’S REVIEW: Il Tramezzino is a must try spot here in LA! They have 2 locations in Studio City and Beverly Hills. They put so much effort and care into their food and it shows. Quality and authenticity is key here and they’re also very attentive to every need with top notch customer service. They had food delivery guys running in and out of this place so you know they’re doing something right. I highly recommend this spot so check it out and let me know what you think. 🤌🏽🔥

Thank you God for allowing me to live this beautiful life 🙏🏽 last week I had the pleasure of visiting the islands of Bonaire and Curaçao. It was so amazing to go experience other cultures on islands I’ve never even heard of but I’m already excited to go back. Thank you to @jodycdiamond and her wonderful team for setting up our TikTok Island Hop trip with so many creative people. Do yourself a favor and book your next vacation to the ABC islands asap! 🏝️

ROD’S REVIEW: Go book your trip to Bonaire and Curaçao asap! These islands are beautiful! Bonaire is a nice desert island with the bluest water and Curaçao is full of life, vibrant color and culture. Go check out the ABC islands for your next vacation and live life to the fullest!
